sections.title: Honest Summary
sections.text: You are Jia Wood (甲木). Personality: ambitious, principled, stubborn, leadership-oriented. Your Day Master is extremely strong (39% element presence, 20% = balanced). You have overwhelming energy. The risk is stagnation and bulldozing over others. Marriage: Your wife star (正財) is ABSENT. This is the single hardest indicator — marriage comes very late, with great difficulty, or through unconventional paths. This is not a death sentence, but it requires conscious effort and the right luck decade. Health: Watch Heart (Fire) — these elements are deficient in your chart. Life lesson: You have abundant energy but it needs direction. Your lesson is channeling power into productive outlets rather than letting it stagnate. Your useful god is Fire (currently at 1.1% — most deficient). Adding Fire brings the chart closest to 20% equilibrium across all five elements. Favorable: Fire, Earth, Metal. Unfavorable: Water, Wood (already excessive). Everything in your life improves when you increase Fire element exposure.
